('chk-specialization-review', 'ph-specialization', 90, 'checkpoint', 'gate', NULL, NULL, 'Specialization Review Gate', 'Review checkpoint for Specialization Tracks. The learner consolidates evidence from Tabular ML Specialist Track, Computer Vision Specialist Track, NLP Specialist Track, MLOps Specialist Track, identifies unresolved prerequisite gaps, and decides whether to continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice before the next roadmap segment.', 'checkpoint', 3, 'advanced', '{"source": "roadmap.sh/machine-learning", "checkpointType": "review", "checkpointPurpose": "phase_review", "reviewMode": "gate", "evidenceRequired": true, "claimLimit": "orientation_and_progress_review_only_not_certification"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Summarize the main concepts and decisions from Specialization Tracks in practical machine learning engineering terms.", "Identify prerequisite gaps, unclear topics, or risks that should be reviewed before moving forward.", "Create a short evidence artifact that links completed roadmap items to what was learned."]'::jsonb, '["List the roadmap items reviewed for this checkpoint.", "Provide one evidence artifact such as notes, a diagram, a lab result, code, queries, screenshots, or a project review.", "Record at least two gaps, risks, or follow-up actions, or explicitly state that no critical gaps were found.", "Use the result to choose one next step: continue, review selected topics, or complete extra practice."]'::jsonb),
('proj-specialization-case-study', 'ph-specialization', 101, 'project', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Required Specialization Case Study', 'Milestone project: Build or document a specialization-focused ML project with technical and product tradeoffs.', 'side', 8, 'advanced', '{"project":true,"projectBrief":"Build or document a specialization-focused ML project with technical and product tradeoffs.","projectKind":"ai_ml_application","projectScope":"focused_milestone","projectPurpose":"Demonstrate the surrounding roadmap segment through a focused milestone artifact.","phaseContext":"Specialization Tracks","deliverable":"a working Specialization Case Study notebook, service, or app with evaluation notes","skillsToPractice":["Specialization Tracks"],"suggestedSteps":["Define the Specialization Case Study scenario, target user or reviewer, and the specific Specialization Tracks concepts it will demonstrate.","Choose the dataset, model, prompt, retrieval source, or tool boundary required by the project brief.","Build the baseline workflow first, then add the AI/ML behavior in a way that can be inspected.","Capture evaluation cases that include successful output, weak output, and at least one failure mode.","Add safeguards, citations, metrics, traces, or manual review notes where the project context requires them.","Document model assumptions, limitations, cost/latency concerns, and what would need review before real use.","Keep the scope focused enough to complete, review, and explain the a working Specialization Case Study notebook, service, or app with evaluation notes."],"expectedEvidence":["a working Specialization Case Study notebook, service, or app with evaluation notes.","README or notes that explain setup, usage, assumptions, and expected output.","Evaluation cases, model/prompt/retrieval configuration, and notes on weak or unsafe outputs.","Validation evidence such as tests, screenshots, logs, query results, metrics, traces, or review notes.","Short reflection on trade-offs, limitations, and one reasonable next improvement."],"reviewFocus":["Does the artifact directly match the project brief?","Can another person run, inspect, or review the result from the provided notes?","Are assumptions, limitations, and trade-offs stated clearly?"],"scopeGuardrails":["Keep the implementation focused on the stated project brief.","Prefer a complete small artifact over a broad unfinished system.","Treat completion as reviewable evidence, not a certification claim."],"claimLimit":"Completion creates reviewable project evidence. It does not certify mastery or guarantee job readiness.","evidenceRequired":true,"optionalPractice":false,"milestone":true,"source":"roadmap.sh/machine-learning","nodeKey":"proj-specialization-case-study"}'::jsonb, true, true, '["Apply Specialization Tracks through a focused Specialization Case Study artifact.","Explain the main design, data, tooling, workflow, or review decisions behind the project.","Validate the result with evidence that another person can inspect.","Document assumptions, limitations, and a concrete follow-up improvement."]'::jsonb, '["The a working Specialization Case Study notebook, service, or app with evaluation notes is available for review.","The Specialization Case Study scope, setup path, input data or scenario, and expected output are documented.","The main workflow runs or can be inspected through a notebook, repository, dashboard, prototype, report, configuration, or case study.","Validation evidence is included and directly relates to the project brief.","The notes identify trade-offs, limitations, and one next improvement without claiming mastery or job readiness."]'::jsonb),
